summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 37995, entitled: "An ordinance appropriating $13,620.15 from the Cedar River Watershed 1917 Utility Bonds Fund of the City of Seattle to the State of Washington for the purpose of paying the judgements, with interest in favor of the State of Washington in the condemnation proceedings instituted under Ordinance No. 37022, authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor, and declaring an emergency."
